message.content: cs.PL, cs.LO, cs.THEORY, cs.DS, cs.SY - This paper deals with type systems and formalisation of communication protocols in a pi-calculus, which are topics that are commonly studied in programming languages (cs.PL) and theoretical computer science (cs.THEORY). The paper also discusses the concept of determinism in typed programs, which is a topic that falls under logic (cs.LO) and data structures (cs.DS). Finally, the paper deals with synchronous communication, which is a topic that falls under systems and control (cs.SY).
